                The Mosselkrakers are a proud group of senior golfers who play
                at Mossel Bay Golf Club every Tuesday and Friday.
            </p>

            <p>
                Members compete in Stableford competitions, Fourball matches,
                Pair competitions and a variety of fun golf formats that keep
                the spirit of friendly rivalry alive.
            </p>

            <p>
                While competition remains important, camaraderie and friendship
                are the true foundations of the group. Members regularly enjoy
                social gatherings including the famous monthly Worsbraai.
            </p>

